        <section class="page-title page-title-layout1 bg-overlay">
            <div class="bg-img"><img src="/unicare-assets/images/page-titles/1.jpg" alt="background"></div>
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-12 col-xl-5">
                        <h1 class="pagetitle__heading">About Unicare Clinic - Your Trusted Bali Medical Clinic</h1>
                        <p class="pagetitle__desc">Experience world-class healthcare at Unicare Clinic, the leading medical clinic in Bali. Our dedicated team of experienced doctors and healthcare professionals is committed to delivering compassionate and personalized care.
                        </p>
                        <div class="d-flex flex-wrap align-items-center">
                            <a href="/unicare-clinic/appointment.html" class="btn btn__primary btn__rounded mr-30">
                                <span>Find A Doctor</span>
                                <i class="icon-arrow-right"></i>
                            </a>
                            <a href="/unicare-clinic/services.html" class="btn btn__white btn__rounded">
                                <span>Our Services</span>
                                <i class="icon-arrow-right"></i>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="about-layout1 pb-0">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-6">
                        <div class="heading-layout2">
                            <h3 class="heading__title mb-40">About Unicare Clinic - Your Trusted Bali Medical Clinic</h3>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-6">
                        <div class="about__Text">
                            <p class="mb-30">As a trusted 24-hour Bali medical clinic, we prioritize your health and well-being with comprehensive healthcare solutions. From general medical consultations to specialized treatments, our modern facilities ensure the highest standards of care. Your safety and comfort are our top priorities.
                            </p>
                            <p class="mb-30">Located conveniently across major areas in Bali, including Kuta, Uluwatu, Ubud, and Nusa Dua, we are always within your reach. Whether you need urgent medical attention or routine health check-ups, our clinics are designed to meet all your healthcare needs. Trust us for accessible and exceptional medical care.</p>
                            <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-30">
                                <a href="/unicare-clinic/doctors-grid.html" class="btn btn__primary btn__outlined btn__rounded mr-30">
                                    Meet Our Doctors</a>
